snippet.title: Evercade Data East 'Collection 1' Cartridge Trailer
snippet.description:
Visit: http://evercade.co.uk/data-east-collection/

The Data East Collection 1 cartridge brings 10 classic Data East games to the Evercade, including: Burger Time, Bad Dudes, Midnight Resistance and more! The cartridge will be supplied in a stunning collectable retro style physical case.

Full games list:

1. Burger Time
2. Fighter's History
3. Midnight Resistance
4. Burnin’ Rubber (Bump & Jump)
5. Karate Champ
6. Joe & Mac 2: Lost in the tropics
7.Side Pocket
8. Magical Drop 2
9. Two Crude Dudes
10. Bad Dudes
